snippet.title: SD Gundam G Generation ETERNAL Teaser Trailer - For App Store / Google Play
snippet.description:
While enjoying a story inspired by the original Gundam works
Players create their own troops beyond the the original work.
G-Generation series

The latest in the series is now available as a smartphone simulation game.

SD Gundam G Generation Eternal

Click here for the official website.
https://gget.ggame.jp/en　

Official SNS is here.
